{"word":"G2169 - εὐχαριστία - eucharistía - yoo-khar-is-tee'-ah - Thankfulness","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐχαριστία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eucharistía</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-khar-is-tee'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Thankfulness</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"நன்றி, ஸ்தோத்திரம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. thankfulness"},{"paragraph":"2. the giving of thanks"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2170 - εὐχάριστος - eucháristos - yoo-khar'-is-tos/2170\">G2170</a>; <i>gratitude</i>; actually <i>grateful language</i> (to God, as an act of worship): - thankfulness, (giving of) thanks (-giving).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2168/2168\">G2168</a>, <a href=\"#/G2169/2169\">G2169</a>, <a href=\"#/G2170/2170\">G2170</a>, <a href=\"#/G4796/4796\">G4796</a>, <a href=\"#/G5463/5463\">G5463</a>, <a href=\"#/G5479/5479\">G5479</a>, <a href=\"#/G5483/5483\">G5483</a>, <a href=\"#/G5484/5484\">G5484</a>, <a href=\"#/G5485/5485\">G5485</a>, <a href=\"#/G5486/5486\">G5486</a>, <a href=\"#/G5487/5487\">G5487</a>, <a href=\"#/G884/884\">G884</a>"}]}